🔹 Router Booting Process (Step by Step)

Jab router on hota hai (power lagate hi), uska process kuch aise hota hai:

1️⃣ POST (Power-On Self Test)

        English: Router checks its hardware (RAM, CPU, interfaces).
        
        Hindi: Jaise computer start hote hi apna hardware check karta hai, router bhi apne parts ko test karta hai.
        👉 Agar hardware kharab ho → error message aayega.

2️⃣ Bootstrap Program Load

        English: Bootstrap is a small code stored in ROM. It decides what to do next (like a guide).
        
        Hindi: Bootstrap ek chhota software hai jo router ko batata hai ki Operating System (IOS) kaha se load karna hai.

3️⃣ Load IOS (Internetwork Operating System)

        English: Router now loads the IOS (its brain) from Flash memory (or TFTP server if needed).
        
        Hindi: Ab router apna IOS software load karta hai jo usko chalata hai. Ye mostly Flash memory me hota hai.

4️⃣ Find Configuration File

        English: Router looks for a configuration file (startup-config) in NVRAM.
        
        Hindi: Router check karta hai ki koi settings/configuration file hai kya NVRAM me (jaise IP addresses, routing info).

5️⃣ Run Configuration

        English: If config file is found → router applies settings.
        
        Hindi: Agar file mil gayi → router wahi purani settings load karega (IP, routes, passwords).
👉 Agar config file nahi mili → router setup mode me chala jayega (basic configuration karne ko bolega).

🔹 Summary in One Line

        POST → Hardware check 🛠️
        
        Bootstrap → Decide IOS kaha se lana hai 📍
        
        Load IOS → Operating System chalu karna 🧠
        
        Load Config → NVRAM se purani settings lana ⚙️

        Router Ready 🚦

⚡ Example: Ye bilkul waise hi hai jaise tumhara computer boot hota hai →

        Hardware check karta hai (POST),
        
        BIOS (Bootstrap) load hota hai,
        
        OS (Windows/Linux = IOS) start hota hai,
        
        Settings apply hoti hain,
        
        Fir use karne ke liye ready ho jaata hai.
